entertaining reading for foodies with mark kurlansky 's reputation as one of the best food writers today , it was only a matter of time before a collection of some of his selections of good food writing came together . & quot ; choice cuts & quot ; is entertaining reading , especially for those who are interested in the history of eating and food . there are few recipes in this book , but this collection is more of a book that you sit down with a cup of coffee or tea after you 've finished the dishes